If the identity search is still processing after 5 seconds:

ID verifications typically only take one or two seconds but, depending on data
provider availability, in certain circumstances it can take longer. To account
for this while still being fault-tolerant, if the identity search creation
takes longer than 5 seconds, the search will be entered into a search queue
which can be retrieved when it is complete.

